For 17years,Naveen Patnaik has ruled Odisha,while other states have marched ahead on parameters of development,Odisha has remained backward.
Odisha can provide power to entire nation but it is deplorable that 41% households in the state do not have electricity connection.
If a Chief Minister cannot provide electricity to his state in 17 years, he does not deserve to stay in power.
Forget jobs,healthcare &power..tribals of Odisha do not even get rice 2times a day,state govt has also failed to provide water to farmlands.
